column5: Who thinks the conditions will be good this weekend? I am unsure if the water will still be too high and that's its pretty cold . Its probably still murky on the east shores I presume?
Just go,thats what my plan is.
x2  Best way to find out is to go take a look.
If I didn't have other plans, I'd be going out...I'd just bring ice melter for the ramp.
